 <scopecontent id="scopecontent-1.8.3">
 <head>Scope and Content</head>
 <p>Collection consists of playbills from Britain, Europe, and the U.S. Includes playbills from various London theaters, some from Glasgow, and one from Dublin. Also includes playbills from California, mostly San Francisco and Los Angeles, and from other states, primarily New York, St. Louis, and Detroit.</p>
 </scopecontent>
